    "text": "<p>This spell makes the duration of certain other spells permanent. You first cast the desired spell and then follow it with the <i>permanency<\/i> spell.<\/p><p>Depending on the spell, you must be of a minimum caster level and must expend a specific gp value of diamond dust as a material component.<\/p><p>You can make the following spells permanent in regard to <b>yourself<\/b>. You cannot cast these spells on other creatures. This application of <i>permanency<\/i> can be dispelled only by a caster of higher level than you were when you cast the spell.<\/p><table border=\"1\"> <caption>Target: Self Only<\/caption> <thead>  <tr>   <th class=\"text\">Spell<\/th>   <th class=\"text\">Minimum Caster Level<\/th>   <th class=\"text\">GP Cost<\/th>   <th class=\"text\">Source<\/th>  <\/tr> <\/thead> <tbody>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Arcane sight<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">11th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">7,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">CRB<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Aura sight<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">11th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">7,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">ACG<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Comprehend languages<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">9th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">2,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">CRB<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Darkvision<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">10th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">5,000 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">CRB<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Detect magic<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">9th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">2,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">CRB<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Enchantment sight<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">9th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">2,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source text\">PC:HotHC<\/td>  <\/tr>  <tr>   <td class=\"text\">Read magic<\/td>   <td class=\"number\">9th<\/td>   <td class=\"money number\">2,500 gp<\/td>   <td class=\"source t